SOLD: Clydesdale Trail, McCormick Ranch, Scottsdale AZ 💯💕
 
I am more than thrilled for my clients who were able to sell their family home in McCormack Ranch and relocate to a larger, newer home in Desert Ridge.
The market may have slowed down...but I certainly haven’t. If you need a professional real estate agent to think outside-of-the-box to sell your current home or buy your next property I am your Gal. ➡️👧
 
$900,000
 
4 Beds
2 Baths
2,745 Square Feet
 
A true gem located on a highly desirable street in Scottsdale’s McCormick Ranch sitting on a large, mature, north-south facing lot with an inviting sparkling pool, fabulous fruit trees and an expanding green with direct access to the nearby communities' network of green belt trails and natural amenities.

I am thrilled to announce that I have joined The Brokery.  I am very excited to work with such an exceptional brokerage whose recent growth has been fueled by a relentless focus on local neighborhoods, neighbors and residents who have referred and championed their business as one of the state’s top residential real estate firms.  As my local markets of focus continue to normalize, Desert Ridge, and the greater Arcadia area will also prove to be difficult for those that aren’t armed with up-to-date trends, data, and sales tactics at a hyperlocal level. At The Brokery, we have all of the marketing firepower and local knowledge to help you beat the market both as a buyer or seller.
